(715, 'Dunlopillo Romero Premium', '', 44765000, '303', '', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 128);"><var style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">H&agrave;ng được b&aacute;n tại Showroom Dunlopillo B2-R5-1 Vincom Mega Mall Royal City 72A Nguyễn Tr&atilde;i, Thanh Xu&acirc;n, H&agrave; Nội từ ng&agrave;y 15/07/2013</var></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 128);"><var style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Nh&acirc;n dịp khai trương qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch được giảm gi&aacute; 20% Chương tr&igrave;nh thực hiện đến 31/08/2013</var></span></p>\r\n<div class="ad-gallery" id="gallery" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<div class="ad-image-wrapper" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 128);"><var style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Ngay b&acirc;y giờ qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; thể đặt h&agrave;ng theo số điện thoại : 04.3793 0913</var></span></div>\r\n	<div class="ad-image-wrapper" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div class="ad-image-wrapper" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div class="ad-image-wrapper" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><span class="short_text" id="result_box" lang="en" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><span class="hps alt-edited" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Products Description</span></span></span>:</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="productContentWrap" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		With the idea taken from a gemstone symbolizing stability, balance and harmony ; Emerald<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n		Premium is designed to offer the perfect&nbsp; balance between comfort and support. As emeralds<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n		also promote health of healing, the delicate style of this new line mattress focuses on offering<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n		a blissful sleeping environment, within which your body and mind heals and recovers from restful rejuvenating sleep.</p>\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n	<div class="ad-gallery" id="gallery" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<div class="ad-image" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 451px; height: 326px; top: 0px; left: 0px;">\r\n				<img height="326" src="http://dunlopilloworld.com/sites/default/files/talasilver01.jpg" style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 600px; display: block;" width="451" /></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="ad-nav" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<div class="ad-thumbs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-size: 14px;">\r\n		Talasilver&trade; latex, the ultimate protection</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		Due to its natural anti-bacterial and anti-fungal properties, silver was the preferred treatment for medical ailments for more than a century. DunlopilloTalasilver&trade; latex incorporates Nano Silver technology to provide the most advanced protection for healthy sleep.</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		Nano Silver is a group of micro-sized (nano) bits of silver that is tested to effectively prevent and kill bacteria. Although invisible to the human eye, Nano Silver is proven to add immeasurably to our well being.</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		Using the two common bacteria &ndash; Staphylococcus aureus and Klebsiella pneumonia, stringent laboratory tests* were performed on DunlopilloTalasilver&trade; latex to determine its bactericidal properties. Results showed no presence or growth of either bacteria.</p>\r\n	<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-size: 14px;">\r\n		The benefits</h3>\r\n	<ul class="ul" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			Bactericidal: Proven to kill bacteria.</li>\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			Non-poisonous</li>\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			Non-allergic: Kind to those with allergies.</li>\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			Unsurpassed support and comfort: Combined with air in an arrangement of interconnecting cells that are uniformed and open.</li>\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			Self-ventilating: The many pincore cells allow air to flow freely, keeping you fresh, dry and cool.</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<i style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">*Tested and certified by Shirley Technologies Ltd. in the UK.</i><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n	<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n	DunlopilloTalasilver&trade; latex meets the British Standard of BS EN ISO 20743: 2007.\r\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">PARALLEL INDIVIDUAL POCKETED SPRING SYSTEM</strong></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		17cm pocket springs are individually created and placed in their respective fabric pockets in a parallel arrangement, bringing optimal comfort as it perfectly adjusts to body contours while minimizing your partner&rsquo;s.</p>\r\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">PLUSH TOP DESIGN</strong></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		This plush top offers the optimal combination of support and comfort to users enhancing the soft, plush and luxurious feel.</p>\r\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">ULTRAFIRM EDGE SUPPORT</strong></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		Designed with UltraFirm frame, this advanced construction allows you<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n		to sleep right to the edge of the bed without rolling off. This increases<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n		the sleeping surface area and the durability of your mattress.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'img/upload/bbb522541cb810dedad04f253bf42c3b.jpg', '', 398, 0, '2013-10-24 10:21:32', '2013-10-24 11:16:53', 1, 1, 'dunlopillo-romero-premium', '', '220x200x34cm, 200x200cm, 180x200x34cm, 160x200x34cm', NULL, NULL, 1, 35812000, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '20%'),
