(723, 'Dunlopillo Cashmerian Luxe', '', 238500000, '303', '', '<div id="productContentWrap" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<var style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 128);">H&agrave;ng được b&aacute;n tại Showroom Dunlopillo B2-R5-1 Royal City 72A Nguyễn Tr&atilde;i, Thanh Xu&acirc;n, H&agrave; Nội từ ng&agrave;y 15/07/2013</span></var></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<var style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 128);">Nh&acirc;n dịp khai trương qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch được giảm gi&aacute; 25%</span></var>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 128);"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Từ ng&agrave;y 26/07/2013 đến hết ng&agrave;y 31/08/2013</em></span></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<var style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 128);">Ngay từ b&acirc;y giờ qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; thể đặt h&agrave;ng theo số điện thoại 04.62620359</span></var></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><span class="short_text" id="result_box" lang="en" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><span class="hps alt-edited" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Products Description</span></span></span>:</strong></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		Cashmerian :&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">A true expression in luxury and comfort.</em></strong></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		Where personal luxury is concerned, Cashmerian Luxe takes the most intimate part of it to greater depth. Fit for royalty, Cashmerian Luxe is crafted with lavish layers of the finest materials, providing you unyielding support and comfort. Incorporating exquisite features such as Smartcel&trade; Clima fibre, Talalay Latex, Talasilver&trade; Latex, Hexa Gel and a Duo Comfort Pocketed System, you can look forward to being whisked away to a world of serenity every time you sleep.</p>\r\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">The ideal temperature throughout the night</strong></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		The new Cashmerian Luxe promises unparallelled comfort through the revolutionary Smartcel&trade; Clima, a technology that incorporates a PCM (Phase Change Material) micro composite of the latest thermo-regulating properties. Developed on a highly scientific level, Smartcel&trade; Clima fibre actively reacts on temperature variations while you sleep.</p>\r\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Improved gel structure for lasting support</strong></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		Hexa Gel takes the aspect of body support to a new level with a top layer of soft, yet extremely strong and resilient elastic gel. Designed to resemble the shape of a honeycomb. This design resists force that comes from the sides, thus ensuring the idyllic sleep surface for reliable long-term health and wellness.</p>\r\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">The Ultimate Protection For Your Health</strong></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		The Cashmerian Luxe comes with Talasilver&trade; latex that incorporates Nano Silver technology, providing you with the most advanced protection for a truly hygienic and healthy sleep experience.</p>\r\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">All your pressure points eased and attended to</strong></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		Beneath the comfort of Smartcel&trade; Clima Silk Cashmere fabric is a Duo Comfort Pocketed System, incorporated to improve blood flow and reduce high pressure spikes that are frequently caused by the motion of tossing and turning during sleep.</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="main-spec" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<div class="award" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; overflow: hidden;">\r\n		<div class="icon" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<div class="images" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<img alt="" class="imagecache imagecache-materials" height="100" src="http://dunlopilloworld.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/materials/in01_1.png" style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 600px; display: block;" title="" width="98" /></div>\r\n			<div class="descri" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Talalay Latex</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n				Superior latex for support, comfort, durability and resistant to dust mite and bacteria.<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n				<div id="productContentWrap" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n					<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-size: 14px;">\r\n						The original Dunlopillo Talalay Latex</h3>\r\n					<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n						Dunlopillo was the first to introduce latex foam mattresses in 1931, and have continued our commitment with great success to a position of industry leadership today.</p>\r\n					<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-size: 14px;">\r\n						The benefits</h3>\r\n					<ul class="ul" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n						<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Superior mattress material</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n							With higher elasticity, latex mattresses cradle your body contours to provide superior support and comfort, ensuring a perfect sleeping position.</li>\r\n						<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Scientifically proven to be healthier</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n							Latex foam is the hygienic ideal for mattress filling, &quot;better than all existing materials and possessing an exceptionally high anti-bacterial activity&quot;, according to Dr. Theo Lammers at the Institute of Hygiene, Gutenberg University in the medical journal, Deutsche MedizinischeWochenschrift 1954.</li>\r\n						<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Ideal for those with respiratory problems</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n							Latex foam mattresses were confirmed to help provide relief from nightly attacks of asthma, according to further research by Drs. Fuchs and Gronemeyer at the Asthma Clinic, Bad Lippsinge in 1956 in the medical journal, MuenchenerMedizinischeWochenschrift 1956.</li>\r\n						<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Minimal disturbance from your sleep partner</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n							Its ability to support your weight independently and localise body movement to one side of the bed allows you to move freely.</li>\r\n						<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Equal for partners of different sizes</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n							A latex mattress can effectively support partners of different weight and height, as it recovers from mattress indentation immediately.</li>\r\n						<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Extremely resilient</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n							Many tests confirm the resilience of latex and its ability to maintain its shape for long-lasting support.</li>\r\n					</ul>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="icon icon-line" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; display: inline-block; width: 14px; height: 14px; line-height: 14px; vertical-align: text-top; background-image: url(http://www.sieuthidem.com/images/glyphicons-halflings.png); background-position: 14px 14px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n			<div class="images" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div class="descri" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Talasilver Latex</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n				Provides support and comfort with Nano Silver technology to eliminate bacteria growth.\r\n				<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n					<div class="node node  clearfix node-type-material" id="node-322" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n						<div class="node-inner" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n							<div class="ad-nav" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n								<div class="ad-thumbs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n									<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n										&nbsp;</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<div id="productContentWrap" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n								<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-size: 14px;">\r\n									Talasilver&trade; latex, the ultimate protection</h3>\r\n								<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n									Due to its natural anti-bacterial and anti-fungal properties, silver was the preferred treatment for medical ailments for more than a century. DunlopilloTalasilver&trade; latex incorporates Nano Silver technology to provide the most advanced protection for healthy sleep.</p>\r\n								<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n									&nbsp;</p>\r\n								<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n									Nano Silver is a group of micro-sized (nano) bits of silver that is tested to effectively prevent and kill bacteria. Although invisible to the human eye, Nano Silver is proven to add immeasurably to our well being.</p>\r\n								<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n									Using the two common bacteria &ndash; Staphylococcus aureus and Klebsiella pneumonia, stringent laboratory tests* were performed on DunlopilloTalasilver&trade; latex to determine its bactericidal properties. Results showed no presence or growth of either bacteria.</p>\r\n								<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-size: 14px;">\r\n									The benefits</h3>\r\n								<ul class="ul" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n									<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n										Bactericidal: Proven to kill bacteria.</li>\r\n									<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n										Non-poisonous</li>\r\n									<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n										Non-allergic: Kind to those with allergies.</li>\r\n									<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n										Unsurpassed support and comfort: Combined with air in an arrangement of interconnecting cells that are uniformed and open.</li>\r\n									<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n										Self-ventilating: The many pincore cells allow air to flow freely, keeping you fresh, dry and cool.</li>\r\n								</ul>\r\n								<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n									<i style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">*Tested and certified by Shirley Technologies Ltd. in the UK.</i><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n									<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n									DunlopilloTalasilver&trade; latex meets the British Standard of BS EN ISO 20743: 2007.</p>\r\n								<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n									&nbsp;</p>\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="award" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; overflow: hidden;">\r\n		<div class="icon" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<div class="images" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<img alt="" class="imagecache imagecache-materials" height="100" src="http://dunlopilloworld.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/materials/in04_1.png" style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 600px; display: block;" title="" width="98" /></div>\r\n			<div class="descri" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Individual Pocketed Spring System</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n				Isolates movement to minimize disturbance to your partner.<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n					<img height="8" src="http://dunlopilloworld.com/sites/all/themes/dunlopillo/images/arrow.gif" style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 600px; display: block;" width="4" />&nbsp;<a href="http://dunlopilloworld.com/individual-pocketed-spring-system-1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-decoration: none;">read more</a></p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<div class="images" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<img alt="" class="imagecache imagecache-materials" height="100" src="http://dunlopilloworld.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/materials/in06_1.png" style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 600px; display: block;" title="" width="98" /></div>\r\n			<div class="descri" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Dunlopillo-Gel</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n				Advanced gel cushioning technology for back support, spinal alignment and pressure relief.<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n					<img height="8" src="http://dunlopilloworld.com/sites/all/themes/dunlopillo/images/arrow.gif" style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 600px; display: block;" width="4" />&nbsp;<a href="http://dunlopilloworld.com/dunlopillo-gel-0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-decoration: none;">read more</a></p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="award" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; overflow: hidden;">\r\n		<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n			<div class="images" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<img alt="" class="imagecache imagecache-materials" height="100" src="http://dunlopilloworld.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/materials/in05_1.png" style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 600px; display: block;" title="" width="98" /></div>\r\n			<div class="descri" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;">Outlast &reg;</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;" />\r\n				Adapts to body&#39;s changing temperature for a more comfortable sleep.</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'img/upload/3da05e47edaf62ef6f9dfc7b4c2cd6e3.jpg', '', 398, 0, '2013-10-24 10:54:14', '2013-10-24 11:16:15', 1, 1, 'dunlopillo-cashmerian-luxe', '', '220x200x42cm, 200x200x42cm, 180x200x42cm, 160x200x42cm, 120x200x42cm', NULL, NULL, 1, 178875000, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '25%');
